<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Imp1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Imp,</orth> subst. youngling (used only by Armado, Holofernes and Pistol): <cit><quote>dear i.</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 1.2.5" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 2, 5</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>Hercules is presented by this i.</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.592" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 592</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>royal i. of fame,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.5.46" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 5, 46</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.1.45" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 1, 45</bibl>.
